hanhinstall - pachanh packages installer
Usage: hanhinstall [options] [action] package

Available actions:
--sync                                    Sync database from remote
--install                                 Install packages <file>
--remove                                  Remove packages
--gen-skel=<path>                         Generate the packages build files
--build=<directory>                       Build all available build files inside a directory
Available options:
--help                                    Print this message"
--version                                 Print version"
--config=<path to config>                 Use a alternative config"
--sysroot=<path>                          Change root directory
--downloader=<command>                    Use another download command
--mirror-dir=<path>                       Use specified mirror directory
--disable-depends                         Disable dependencies check

Notes: 
--install option cannot be used with --remove option.
--build=<directory> won't build specified packages. Remove unnecessary packages first.
